<SceneText>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>シェリア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cheria</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>行ってしまったな、デューク……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So Duke's gone his own way.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>人間を滅ぼす事
思い直してくれたのかしら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wonder if he's decided against destroying humanity.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>きっと大丈夫さ。
シェリアの心は通じたはずだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sure it'll be okay.
Your feelings seem to have gotten through to him.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだと嬉しいわ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm glad if that's the case.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>このエターナルソードは……破壊しよう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Eternal Sword... We should destroy it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいの？
持ち帰るのが国からの命令でしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is that alright?
Didn't the government give an order to bring it back?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいんだ。
やはりこんな力は誰にも必要ない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's fine. In the end, nobody needs this kind of power.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>大切だと思い合える誰かがいれば
人は生きていけるんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As long as people have something precious to them,
they'll be able to survive.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ええ、そうね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, you're right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>アスベル。
これからも、私はあなたを守るから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Asbel. From here on, I'm going to protect you, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、頼む。
俺も最後までシェリアを守り抜いてみせるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, please do.
I'll also be there to protect you until the very end.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
